  "title": "(6mths Internship) Junior Marketing Associate",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>About the Role:</strong></u></p>\n<p>We’re seeking a <em>proactive and energetic</em> Marketing Intern to support our local marketing efforts through in-person activations, events, and community engagement. This role is ideal for someone who <em>loves interacting with people, thrives in dynamic environments</em>, and wants hands-on experience in experiential marketing.  </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Assist in planning and executing marketing strategies.</p>\n<p>- Engage directly with customers to gather feedback and generate leads.</p>\n<p>- Help bridge client and customer relationships.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ideal Candidate:</p>\n<p>- Enjoys teamwork but can also take initiative independently.  </p>\n<p>- Adaptable! Able handle last-minute event changes or challenges.  </p>\n<p>- Creative problem-solver with a passion for brand storytelling. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Perks &amp; Benefits:</p>\n<p>- Hands-on experience. EARN WHILE YOU EARN!!!</p>\n<p>- Networking opportunities with local businesses and marketing professionals.  </p>\n<p>- Free gym membership</p>\n<p>- Overseas opportunities and development workshops.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
